 backgorund-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}

Q how do you create showdow effect?
.Crated a ::shadow effect using the box-shadow property for element shadows or for text shodow
box-shadow: h-offset v-offset blur spread color;
.h-offset: The :horizontal offset of the shodow
.v-offset: The vertical off set of the shodow 
.blur(optional): the spread radius 
. Color(:optional): The color of the ::shadow
Selector {
    box-showdow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

