Q what is the animations-timing-functions property?
.The animations-timing-functions property specifics the speed curve of the animations 
. common values include linear ease ease-in ease-in out
@keyframes example {
    0%{backgorund-color: red; left: 0px; top: 0px}
    50%{background-color; yellow left: 200px top : 0p;}
    100%{background-color blue; left: 200px, top: 200px;}
}
.element {
    positions relatives;
    animation example 5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

